caption: We opted for the sea plane ride out to island. Right decision. Except I got put in the middle seat to preserve leg room? So I kind of had to lean over the shoulder of the stranger next to me to see anything. This picture is actually from our bonus day where we canoed around some of the bays on the island. The plane lined up way too perfectly.

Matt walking in the woods - classic. I think around here is where we got into some pretty dense foliage (that's ~90% of the island actually) and freaked out a moose. We were all a little tired and dazed and then about 5 feet off the trail a 2000 pound unit just rampaged away. Pretty cool. Probably should be a lil more observant.
